<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَتَكْفِينُهُ فَرْضُ كَفَايةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَجِبُ لِحَقِّ الله تَعَالَى وَلِحَقِّهِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- ثَوْبٌ وَاحِدٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- لَا يَصِفُ البَشَرَةَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- يَسْتُرُ جَمِيعَهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَسُنَّ تَكْفِينُ رَجُلٍ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- فِي ثَلَاثِ لَفَائِفَ بِيضٍ مِنْ قُطْنٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَكُرِهَ فِي أَكْثَرَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- يُبْسَطُ بَعْضُهَا عَلَى بَعْضٍ بَعْدَ تَبْخِيرِهَا بِنَحْوِ عُودٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَتُجْعَلُ الظَّاهِرَةُ أَحْسَنَهَا، وَالحَنُوطُ فِيمَا بَيْنَهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- ثُمَّ يُوضَعُ عَلَيْهَا مُسْتَلْقِيًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- ثُمَّ يُرَدُّ طَرَفُ اللِّفَافَةِ العُلْيَا مِنَ الجَانِبِ الأَيْسَرِ عَلَى شِقِّهِ الأَيْمَنِ، ثُمَّ الأَيْمَنِ عَلَى الأَيْسَرِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- ثُمَّ الثَّانِيَةِ ثُمَّ الثَّالِثَةِ كَذَلِكَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>